data.description: **2.375% interest rate, payments of $1,980 PITI - ASSUMABLE VA LOAN - ask for more details*** Built in 2013, nestled in a quite cul de sac, this home has everything you’ve been looking for! Brand new, gorgeous hardwood stairway. Open kitchen with all new, 2023 Wifi compatible appliances, pantry, and granite counters. Stunning waterproof flooring throughout the entire 1st floor, installed in 2023. Coffee bar with floating shelves. Gas fireplace. Spacious primary suite with 2 walk-in closets and an updated private bath. Fenced backyard with large patio & storage shed. 2 car garage. Dual zone HVAC. Convenient to I264, area bases, Hilltop shopping, dining, and oceanfront.
